              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Multi-channel review collection and monitoring</li>
                <li>Webchat, SMS, and survey workflows</li>
                <li>Sentiment analysis across review sources</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Priced for multi-location operators</li>
                <li>Annual contracts standard</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Local chains where review volume is the primary growth lever.</div>
            <a href="https://birdeye.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">07</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Canva</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best DIY marketing design</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$15<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Pro plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Templates for every local marketing format</li>
                <li>Brand kit so social posts stay consistent</li>
                <li>Free plan handles 80% of solo-owner design needs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Still requires you to design and publish each post</li>
                <li>Limited automation for batch creation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Owners who want to create social, flyers, and ads in-house.</div>
