              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best affordable SEO suite</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$65<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Essential plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Keyword research, backlinks, on-page audits</li>
                <li>Local rank tracking included</li>
                <li>Multi-project support for service-area chains</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Local-specific features are lighter than BrightLocal</li>
                <li>Steeper learning curve for non-SEO owners</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators who want broad SEO plus local in one dashboard.</div>
            <a href="https://seranking.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">09</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Podium</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best SMS reviews and messaging</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$249<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Essentials plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>SMS-based review requests with high conversion</li>
